-- Icahn offers $20 mln to keep Atlantic City Trump casino open
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bengaluru
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 03:05PM EST
-- None



Dec 18 (Reuters) - Billionaire investor Carl Icahn offered to lend $20 million to help bankrupt casino operator Trump Entertainment Resorts Inc keep its Trump Taj Mahal casino in Atlantic City open.

